sly difficult to measure, and there is no single source of data that provides a complete picture of the crime. On RAINN&rsquo;s website, we have tried to select the most reliable source of statistics for each topic. The primary data source we use is the National Crime Victimization Survey (NCVS), which is an annual study conducted by the Justice Department. To conduct NCVS, researchers interview tens of thousands of Americans each year to learn about crimes that they&rsquo;ve experienced. Based on those interviews, the study provides estimates of the total number of crimes, including those that were not reported to police. While NCVS has a number of limitations (most importantly, children under age 12 are not included), overall, it is the most reliable source of crime statistics in the U.S."},{"pid":"de055b005752d315c99766e8366388097efb856b","tid":905304,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"663f027c4aabbc4f77f4ccc5a4e5d043cef459a5","tid":905304,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"內褲相呢????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.independent.co.uk/life-style/women/thisisnotconsent-women-underwear-rape-trial-ireland-activists-hashtag-a8633236.html%3Famp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Fwomen%2Fthisisnotconsent-women-underwear-rape-trial-ireland-activists-hashtag-a8633236.html%253Famp&d=s3MI7VAOkm5bhBhmo8PddF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0f934887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.independent.co.uk/life-style/women/thisisnotconsent-women-underwear-rape-trial-ireland-activists-hashtag-a8633236.html%3Famp</a>"},{"pid":"352c6ae02512dbbe791ea0b787d8de9fc3d39023","tid":905304,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quot